      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offered in truly immaculate condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, having undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our uncompromising standards for aesthetic and mechanical excellence. With a finish that retains its original showroom luster and an interior that remains untouched by wear, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning driver. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that performs as flawlessly as it presents.",
      "price": 48500.0,
