    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a masterfully preserved E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example boasts a factory-spec Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a pristine M-variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the critical rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement have been completed to ensure peak structural and rotational integrity. The suspension retains its original kinematic precision, offering unparalleled feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. Zero fluid seepage, a perfectly indexed valvetrain, and an immaculate undercarriage define this collector-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
