      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its showroom-fresh aroma; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians\u2014all service records are meticulously organized and ready for review. This is a time-capsule quality vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
